{"tid":894056,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"福建洩7噸「毒碳九」政府隱瞞 重創漁港多人送院","createTime":"2018-11-08T06:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T06:03:51.000Z","uid":71708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"94db2b52ec9ede6ca74e095483fca9c238672d83","tid":894056,"uid":71708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:03:51.000Z","msg":"福建泉州市爆發嚴重生態災難！福建東港石油化工公司的船隻，周日（4日）在泉州市泉港區碼頭進行裝卸操作時，因軟管墊片老化、破損，導致近7噸化工原料「碳九」洩漏。有傳，已有村民因接觸洩漏物後身體不適入院，甚至有人因掉入污染海域被送進醫院ICU，當地漁排損失嚴重。有指，「碳九」組成份子複雜，沒法分解，同時易於吸入人體，比毒藥還毒。當局事後卻企圖掩飾事件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181108/58887655\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181108%2F58887655&d=Ka4QYMh6GiHTsAA8ISVHEmxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=12c20300\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181108%2F58887655&h=806cdcc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181108/58887655</a><br />\n<br />\n大陸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}